Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我必须要去做一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.32,0:17:00.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But on my way there, I forgot what I was supposed to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.32,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是在去那里的路上，我忘记了应该做什么
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mr. Agah...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿加先生
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.64,0:17:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Excuse my bluntness, but you'd had a heart attack.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.64,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}原谅我的直言不讳，但你得了心脏病
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.44,0:17:13.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You were in the hospital. What could've been so urgent?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.44,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你在医院里有什么紧急的事？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.12,0:17:18.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was my daughter Zuhal's birthday. I had to get her a present.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.12,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是我女儿祖哈尔的生日，我有礼物要送给她
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.44,0:17:22.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Your daughter's here? - I'm here now.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.44,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你的女儿在这里？-我现在在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Looking for a job.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找工作
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Still haven't found one.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么都没找到
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not sure what I'll do.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不知道我该怎么办
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd like to meet her.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想见见她
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We haven't even spoken on the phone. - I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我们甚至都没有打电话 -我知道
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll come by unannounced, you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道我会不请自来的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这不是世界的尽头
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- If you're unhappy, then get divorced. - I guess that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-如果你不开心，那就离婚 -我想这就是我们要做的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.52,0:17:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told Mebrure so many times to divorce him, but she wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.52,0:17:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我跟梅布鲁雷说过很多次让她离婚，但她不听
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We don't listen, sometimes. - Did it both to herself and to us.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-人们有时候就是不听 -自找苦吃
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I was collateral damage, as well. - My mom and dad were miserable.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-对我也有附带伤害 -我的父母都很痛苦
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My dumb sister.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我愚蠢的妹妹
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Being dumb isn't good. - I'm in love, she said.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-装傻是不好的 -我恋爱了，她说
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I'm not even in love. - Your mom was so naive. 
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我根本没有恋爱 -你妈妈太天真了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- She would believe anything.  - I don't believe, though!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-她什么都相信 -但我不相信！
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So what?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I used to lie all the time, doc.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我以前一直撒谎，医生
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When I was young.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我小的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.72,0:18:16.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I used to lie so often, it was second nature to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.72,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经常撒谎，这对我来说是第二天性
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was almost a mania.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快要疯了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mebrure used to believe anything I'd say.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}梅布鲁雷曾经相信我会说的话
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Deceiving her started feeling horrible.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}后来欺骗她让我感到害怕
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hated myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我恨自己
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I promised I'd never lie to her again.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我保证不会再对她说谎
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.32,0:18:36.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd be as honest with everyone else as I was with myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.32,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会像对待自己一样诚实对待其他人
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Alas...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唉……
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Once I was cursed with this disease...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦我被这种疾病诅咒
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This forgetting disease called Alzheimer's...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这种称之为阿尔茨海默氏病的让人遗忘的疾病
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's when I started lying again.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我又开始撒谎了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know what's the worst part about being a liar?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道做为骗子最糟糕的是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.16,0:18:56.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Having to remember all the lies.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.16,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}必须记住所有的谎言
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我现在该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.48,0:19:05.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Call your cousin. We can call him together.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.48,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给你表哥打电话，我们可以一起打电话给他
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.08,0:19:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He'll find you a job that suits you. OK?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.08,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他会找到适合你的工作，好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You don't need your father. I'm right here for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不需要留在你父亲身边，我就在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's the one who needs us.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是他需要我们
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's never accepted it, but he's always been the one who needs us.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他一直都不承认，但他才是需要我们的人
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He thought he could do no wrong. 
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他以为他不会做错事
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.28,0:19:31.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mebrure gave him everything she had.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.28,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}梅布鲁雷把一切都给了他
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I'm losing my personality.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我正在失去我的人格
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's too much to bear.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}太让人受不了了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Here's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来我们这样做
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You can't bear the truth, you lie. - Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你不能忍受真相，你在说谎 -是的
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We'll discover that moment together. - How are we going to do that?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我们会一起发现那一刻的 -我们怎么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The moment you started running from reality.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从现实出发的那一刻
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And why you keep running.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及为什么你一直在逃避
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's what we'll go looking for.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就是我们要寻找的
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I don't know why.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我不知道为什么
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You might not know.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可能不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But your memory does.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你的记忆知道
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ask your memory.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}问问你的记忆
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go into the past.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}回顾过去
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go to the places that remind you of your past.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去那些能让您回想起过去的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Whatever it is that's scaring you
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管是什么使你恐惧
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}is hidden in your past.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都隐藏在你的过去
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Find it, Mr. Agah.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找到它，阿加先生
Dialogue: 2,0:20:19.64,0:20:24.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Find the first truth that terrified you.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:19.64,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找到令你恐惧的真相
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}INCOMING CALL ATES ARBAY
Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿提斯来电
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, Ates?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂，阿提斯？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Is it time yet?{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}到时间了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Time for what?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么时间？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You've promised me an interview. Can we do it tonight?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您答应我的访谈，今晚可以做吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm busy, Ates. Another time.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我很忙，再约时间吧
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't let you down the last time you called.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}上次你找我的时候我可没让你失望哦
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fine. Where do we meet?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好吧，我们在哪里见面？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Give me some space, please.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请给我一些空间，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Huh? - Take off.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-嗯？-走开
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Take off where?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm expecting someone. There's an empty seat over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在等人，那边也有座位
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我哪都不去！
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My dearly departed wife will be here soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我亲爱的亡妻很快就要来了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go on.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去吧
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mebrure!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}梅布鲁雷!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.88,0:22:24.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mebrure!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.88,0:22:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}梅布鲁雷!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I saw that.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我看见了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't you have enough?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还没拍够吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.88,0:22:56.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't look into the camera. Look over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.88,0:22:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要看镜头  看那边
Dialogue: 2,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's the last one.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很快结束了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.72,0:23:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.72,0:23:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就这样
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.64,0:23:09.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Keep that pose.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.64,0:23:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}保持这个姿势
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Is it done?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.92,0:23:16.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.92,0:23:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Stay just like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}保持住
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就这样
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Stay...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}别动
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.20,0:23:24.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Almost there...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.20,0:23:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快好了……
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've got it.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拍完了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Finally.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总算好了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's get started on that interview.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们开始这次访谈吧
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Deva?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}德瓦？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.04,0:23:48.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where have you been, Deva?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.04,0:23:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你去哪了？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told my mom I was going out.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我告诉妈妈我要出去
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She didn't ask where you'd be?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她没有问你会去哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.28,0:23:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I don't explain myself anymore. - Who did you take after, I wonder.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.28,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我不再为自己辩解了 -我不知道你像谁
Dialogue: 2,0:23:59.84,0:24:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You're so weird. - I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:59.84,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你好奇怪 -我知道
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.48,0:24:05.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.48,0:24:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道……
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.80,0:24:12.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've been hearing about
Dialogue: 2,0:24:06.80,0:24:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我经常听说
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.44,0:24:14.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}increased drug use among teenagers.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.44,0:24:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青少年吸毒人数一直在增加
Dialogue: 2,0:24:14.52,0:24:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You don't do that, right. - Of course not, grandpa.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:14.52,0:24:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你不吸毒，对吧？ -当然不吸
Dialogue: 2,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good. That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很好  很好
Dialogue: 2,0:24:20.96,0:24:22.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How about booze?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:20.96,0:24:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Only if you're buying.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你买我就喝
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.32,0:24:28.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've got it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.32,0:24:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道了，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.60,0:24:34.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I want to speak to your former colleagues, as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.60,0:24:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还想跟你以前的同事聊聊
Dialogue: 2,0:24:35.64,0:24:37.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From the company you used to work for.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:35.64,0:24:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你曾经工作过的公司
Dialogue: 2,0:24:38.20,0:24:40.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can ask me whatever you'd like to know.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:38.20,0:24:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你想知道什么可以直接问我
Dialogue: 2,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:44.76,0:24:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because I know them all, but none of them know me.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:44.76,0:24:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我了解他们，但没人了解我
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.12,0:24:52.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fine. Tell me something you'd like to tell me.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.12,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很好，告诉我一些你想告诉我的事
Dialogue: 2,0:24:52.96,0:24:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's the only question that fits someone like you.
Dialogue: 2,0:24:52.96,0:24:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是唯一适合你的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:24:58.28,0:25:00.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What would you like to say, Nevra?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:58.28,0:25:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你想告诉我什么事？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:02.64,0:25:04.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What have you been up to today?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:02.64,0:25:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天做了些什么啊？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.88,0:25:06.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.88,0:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.60,0:25:11.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I went to the place where I proposed to your grandmother. It was 40 years ago.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.60,0:25:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我去了40年前我向你祖母求婚的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:25:12.60,0:25:14.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:12.60,0:25:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- 谢谢你 -不客气
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.40,0:25:15.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Though.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.40,0:25:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然
Dialogue: 2,0:25:17.72,0:25:19.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't propose this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:17.72,0:25:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这次没有求婚
Dialogue: 2,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想说什么
Dialogue: 2,0:25:29.96,0:25:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Is that I'm going to get that killer.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:29.96,0:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要抓到那个杀手
Dialogue: 2,0:25:32.44,0:25:34.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wherever he runs to.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:32.44,0:25:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论他跑到哪里
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.92,0:25:37.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wherever he hides.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.92,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论他躲在哪里
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.64,0:25:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm going to find him, and arrest him.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.64,0:25:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我都要找到他并逮捕他
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.04,0:25:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.04,0:25:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不相信我吗
Dialogue: 2,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I don't believe in anything anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我什么都不相信了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.12,0:25:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I don't even believe in myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.12,0:25:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我甚至不再相信自己
Dialogue: 2,0:25:52.12,0:25:54.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I so need to believe in someone.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:52.12,0:25:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是我需要相信一个人
Dialogue: 2,0:25:55.36,0:25:59.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've been spending my years in the back pages of the newspaper
Dialogue: 2,0:25:55.36,0:25:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我多年来一直在报纸的封底上度过
Dialogue: 2,0:25:59.16,0:26:00.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in that DJ booth,
Dialogue: 2,0:25:59.16,0:26:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在那个DJ位上
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.44,0:26:06.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}at those receptions I attend just to get fucked up,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.44,0:26:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在那些招待会上
Dialogue: 2,0:26:06.40,0:26:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}at the shitty premieres of lame-ass movies.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:06.40,0:26:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在烂片的首映式上
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.76,0:26:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Feels like I'm rotting from the inside.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.76,0:26:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感觉就像我由内而外腐烂
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.20,0:26:16.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't even bear to look in the direction of those photos.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.20,0:26:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我甚至不忍心看那些照片的方向
Dialogue: 2,0:26:19.04,0:26:21.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You still keep them up.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:19.04,0:26:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你还留着它们
Dialogue: 2,0:26:22.68,0:26:24.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They're still there.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:22.68,0:26:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还在那里
Dialogue: 2,0:26:27.12,0:26:30.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told a lie that day. Maybe the first lie of my whole life.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:27.12,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那天我说了一个谎言，也许是我一生中的第一个谎言
Dialogue: 2,0:26:31.76,0:26:33.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"Mebrure," I said,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:31.76,0:26:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“ 梅布鲁雷，”我说，
Dialogue: 2,0:26:33.40,0:26:35.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"I'll make you happy."
Dialogue: 2,0:26:33.40,0:26:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会让你幸福
Dialogue: 2,0:26:36.80,0:26:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"Mebrure, take my hand, and let's get up off this bench,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:36.80,0:26:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“拉着我的手，让我们从凳子上站起来
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.24,0:26:45.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}and -excuse my French-let's get the fuck out of here."
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.24,0:26:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们他妈的离开这里” 原谅我说了脏话
Dialogue: 2,0:26:45.88,0:26:47.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Without a care in the world.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:45.88,0:26:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有一点牵挂
Dialogue: 2,0:26:48.96,0:26:49.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Or...
Dialogue: 2,0:26:48.96,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}或者
Dialogue: 2,0:26:51.56,0:26:53.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"Mebrure, forget you ever knew me..."
Dialogue: 2,0:26:51.56,0:26:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“宝贝，忘了你曾经认识我”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:53.56,0:26:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm not made for marriage.
Dialogue: 2,0:26:53.56,0:26:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“我不是个适合结婚的人”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:57.08,0:26:58.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"I'll only make you unhappy."
Dialogue: 2,0:26:57.08,0:26:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“我只会给你带来不幸”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.04,0:27:01.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.04,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}像这样
Dialogue: 2,0:27:03.84,0:27:06.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can't hold your liquor at all, can you?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:03.84,0:27:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你根本不能喝酒，是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.40,0:27:08.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're already seeing double. Where are you...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.40,0:27:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你已经看重影了，你在哪……
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.08,0:27:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go talk to her. Go on.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.08,0:27:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去跟她聊天吧
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.20,0:27:15.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Think about what you're going to say. You'll kick yourself later otherwise.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.20,0:27:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想好了再说话，不然你会后悔的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:24.08,0:27:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A miserable soul, desperate for attention.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:24.08,0:27:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一个悲惨的灵魂，渴望得到关注
Dialogue: 2,0:27:27.76,0:27:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The biggest favor you can do for such a sociopath is to talk about him.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:27.76,0:27:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你能为这样的反社会变态做的最大的帮助就是谈论他
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.16,0:27:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But you've been on this case ever since the murders started.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.16,0:27:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是，自谋杀案发生以来，您一直在关注这个案件
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.72,0:27:37.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Isn't that a favor to him, then?{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.72,0:27:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那不是对他有利吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I'm a journalist.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是记者
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.48,0:27:41.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I have to inform the public.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.48,0:27:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我必须通知公众
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.88,0:27:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ates, aren't you afraid at all that the murderer will target you?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.88,0:27:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿提斯，你一点都不害怕凶手会把你作为目标吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:46.96,0:27:48.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Look...{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:46.96,0:27:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看
Dialogue: 2,0:27:48.52,0:27:50.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Just like he has his eyes on me,{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:48.52,0:27:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就像他看着我一样
Dialogue: 2,0:27:50.80,0:27:52.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have my eyes on the perimeter of my house.
Dialogue: 2,0:27:50.80,0:27:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也能在房子周围看到你
Dialogue: 2,0:27:54.44,0:27:56.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Remember, no one can turn invisible.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:54.44,0:27:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}记住，没有人可以隐身
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.00,0:28:02.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Least of all someone so deranged.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.00,0:28:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}至少如此疯狂的人不会
Dialogue: 2,0:28:12.64,0:28:14.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is what I do, you see.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:12.64,0:28:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这就是我所做的，你看到了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.40,0:28:18.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm in show business.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.40,0:28:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在做演员
Dialogue: 2,0:28:18.24,0:28:22.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The show serves one purpose only... To make people forget.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:18.24,0:28:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}表演只不过是为了让人们忘记
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.76,0:28:24.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm in the forgetting business.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.76,0:28:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我正在忘记事情
Dialogue: 2,0:28:25.04,0:28:28.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- You're being too harsh on yourself. - It's how it works.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:25.04,0:28:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-你对自己太苛刻了-这就是它的运作方式
Dialogue: 2,0:28:28.64,0:28:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's say there's a massacre somewhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:28.64,0:28:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}假设某处发生大屠杀
Dialogue: 2,0:28:31.56,0:28:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's an assassination, but the assassin never gets caught.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:31.56,0:28:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}发生一次暗杀，但刺客从未被抓住
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I make people forget about them.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我能让人们忘记他们
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.08,0:28:40.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Has there been a huge fraud? Call for me and I'll make them forget.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.08,0:28:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}发生过大型诈骗案吗？找我，我会让他们忘记
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.00,0:28:43.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How? How do you make them forget?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.00,0:28:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么做？如何使他们忘记？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:43.48,0:28:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With stories such as this one about the murderer.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:43.48,0:28:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}像这样一个关于凶手的故事
Dialogue: 2,0:28:47.96,0:28:49.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I spin a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:47.96,0:28:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我编了一个童话故事
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.96,0:28:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They all listen with bated breath.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.96,0:28:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家都屏息静听
Dialogue: 2,0:28:53.24,0:28:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He gets caught and another one emerges.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:53.24,0:28:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他被抓了之后另一个人出现了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.32,0:28:57.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He gets caught, and another one.
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.32,0:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又被抓了，然后又出现一个
Dialogue: 2,0:28:57.84,0:29:01.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I tell all their stories. But you know what I don't do?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:57.84,0:29:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我给他们讲故事，但是你知道我不做什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.60,0:29:05.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How come so many people are licensed to carry guns?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.60,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么这么多人可以携带枪支?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.72,0:29:09.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How come people can access guns so easily?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.72,0:29:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么人们可以如此轻易地获得枪支?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.24,0:29:11.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I never talk about that.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.24,0:29:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我从没说过
Dialogue: 2,0:29:12.40,0:29:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You got it?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:12.40,0:29:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.16,0:29:18.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you want to make people forget about the gun,
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.16,0:29:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你想让人们忘记枪
Dialogue: 2,0:29:19.12,0:29:22.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}all you have to do is talk about the victim.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:19.12,0:29:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你所要做的就是谈论受害者
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.64,0:29:30.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I'm not doing it anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.64,0:29:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我不再这样做了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:32.36,0:29:34.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've had it up to here.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:32.36,0:29:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}到此为止
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.00,0:29:39.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What will you do?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.00,0:29:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:41.28,0:29:42.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}May I curse?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:41.28,0:29:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以讲脏话吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.52,0:29:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll fuck them up.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.52,0:29:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会干他妈的
Dialogue: 2,0:29:48.60,0:29:50.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I won't let people forget.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:48.60,0:29:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不会让人们忘记
Dialogue: 2,0:29:52.04,0:29:53.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When did you decide on that?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:52.04,0:29:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你什么时候决定的?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.44,0:29:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.44,0:29:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.72,0:29:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As I was shooting you, to be precise.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.72,0:29:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}准确地说，当我给你拍照时
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.64,0:30:32.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're so sweet.
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.64,0:30:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好骚啊
Dialogue: 2,0:30:54.12,0:30:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The car...
Dialogue: 2,0:30:54.12,0:30:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}车！
Dialogue: 2,0:32:11.48,0:32:12.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zuhal...
Dialogue: 2,0:32:11.48,0:32:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祖哈尔...
Dialogue: 2,0:32:13.20,0:32:14.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:13.20,0:32:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直在想
Dialogue: 2,0:32:15.32,0:32:17.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We should get you a place.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:15.32,0:32:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们应该给你找个地方
Dialogue: 2,0:32:18.64,0:32:20.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A place of your own.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:18.64,0:32:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}属于你自己的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:32:20.36,0:32:23.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'd both be more comfortable that way.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:20.36,0:32:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那样你们俩会更舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:32:23.32,0:32:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He'll have his own room, at least.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:23.32,0:32:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他至少会有自己的房间
Dialogue: 2,0:32:25.72,0:32:28.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can cover the rent until you get a job.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:25.72,0:32:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我能负担租金直到你找到工作
Dialogue: 2,0:32:29.08,0:32:34.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When you said you'd been thinking, I thought you'd be like...
Dialogue: 2,0:32:29.08,0:32:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当你说你一直在想的时候，我以为你会像
Dialogue: 2,0:32:34.84,0:32:38.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"Let's sell the apartment downstairs and get you a place of your own."
Dialogue: 2,0:32:34.84,0:32:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“我把楼下的公寓卖了，给你找个地方住。”
Dialogue: 2,0:32:38.88,0:32:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:38.88,0:32:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}像这样
Dialogue: 2,0:32:42.64,0:32:44.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's not like I haven't been doing that.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:42.64,0:32:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不是没想过
Dialogue: 2,0:32:44.92,0:32:47.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Number four, covered your high school.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:44.92,0:32:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}四号房间，用于支付你高中的费用
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.92,0:32:49.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Number six, your college.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.92,0:32:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}六号，大学的费用
Dialogue: 2,0:32:50.00,0:32:53.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Number seven, your master's in London.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:50.00,0:32:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}七号，你的伦敦硕士学位
Dialogue: 2,0:32:53.08,0:32:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Number three, as you know, went towards your mother's treatment.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:53.08,0:32:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如你所知，三号支付了你母亲的治疗费用
Dialogue: 2,0:32:56.68,0:32:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm all alone in this huge building now.
Dialogue: 2,0:32:56.68,0:32:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我现在一个人在这个巨大的大楼里
Dialogue: 2,0:33:00.96,0:33:06.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- We still have Number eight, though. - I told you I rent that out.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:00.96,0:33:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-不过我们还有八号 -我告诉你我把它租出去了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:07.56,0:33:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We can tell the tenants we need to sell it. I can talk to them.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:07.56,0:33:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们可以告诉租户我们需要卖掉，可以和他们交谈
Dialogue: 2,0:33:12.96,0:33:15.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can't talk to them. They're using it for storage.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:12.96,0:33:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不能跟他们谈，他们在用房间做仓库
Dialogue: 2,0:33:15.64,0:33:17.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They live abroad.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:15.64,0:33:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他们住在国外
Dialogue: 2,0:33:17.16,0:33:20.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can call them, then. Just give me their number.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:17.16,0:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以打电话给他们，给我他们的电话
Dialogue: 2,0:33:20.60,0:33:23.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Of course. We can sell this apartment, as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:20.60,0:33:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然我们也可以卖这套公寓
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.68,0:33:25.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can put me in a home.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.68,0:33:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你可以把我放在家里
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.52,0:33:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even better, you can put me out on the street.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.52,0:33:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也可以把我扔到大街上
Dialogue: 2,0:33:28.16,0:33:30.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you realize how selfish you sound?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:28.16,0:33:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道你听起来有多自私吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.88,0:33:33.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This building is named after your mother.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.88,0:33:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这座建筑以你母亲的名字命名
Dialogue: 2,0:33:34.28,0:33:36.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How can you be so ready to let it go?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:34.28,0:33:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你怎么能这么轻易放手？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:37.04,0:33:39.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We should be grateful to my departed grandfather, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:37.04,0:33:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们应该感谢我已故的祖父，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:40.40,0:33:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For giving this building to my mother.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:40.40,0:33:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谢谢他把这栋楼交给我妈妈
Dialogue: 2,0:33:43.16,0:33:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What would we do if he hadn't?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:43.16,0:33:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果没有他我们该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:46.24,0:33:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What would you do? What would I? What would Deva?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:46.24,0:33:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你怎么办？我怎么办？德瓦怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.12,0:33:51.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Say what you mean to say.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.12,0:33:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}说出来
Dialogue: 2,0:33:52.24,0:33:54.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What is it you'd like to say, exactly?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:52.24,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您到底想说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:56.04,0:33:58.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't stick your nose where it doesn't belong.
Dialogue: 2,0:33:56.04,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要多管闲事
Dialogue: 2,0:33:59.80,0:34:02.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}See how I don't stick my nose into your business?
Dialogue: 2,0:33:59.80,0:34:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}学学我，从不多管闲事
Dialogue: 2,0:34:02.24,0:34:06.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}See how I never ask about why you got divorced from your husband?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:02.24,0:34:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我从没问过你为什么与丈夫离婚？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:06.52,0:34:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}See how I keep my mouth shut? How about you try it out for once?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:06.52,0:34:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}学我怎么闭嘴，你尝试一下如何？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:09.20,0:34:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ask me, dad.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:09.20,0:34:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}问我啊
Dialogue: 2,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ask me. Why don't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}问什么不问呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:15.00,0:34:16.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Why don't you ask?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:15.00,0:34:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你为什么不问？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:18.68,0:34:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ask me why Deva and I came here.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:18.68,0:34:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}问我为什么德瓦和我来这里
Dialogue: 2,0:34:22.92,0:34:25.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ask me why he wants to get divorced.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:22.92,0:34:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}问我为什么他要离婚
Dialogue: 2,0:34:26.64,0:34:29.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Come on! But you won't, will you?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:26.64,0:34:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}来吧！但是你不会问，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:29.28,0:34:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know why you won't?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:29.28,0:34:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道为什么你不会问吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:31.12,0:34:34.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because you hate listening to other people's problems.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:31.12,0:34:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为你讨厌听别人的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:34:34.84,0:34:37.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's the thing you hate the most.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:34.84,0:34:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是你最讨厌的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:34:37.36,0:34:40.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Someone telling you of their troubles.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:37.36,0:34:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}别人告诉你他们的麻烦事
Dialogue: 2,0:34:41.12,0:34:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Dad...
Dialogue: 2,0:34:41.12,0:34:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸
Dialogue: 2,0:34:42.68,0:34:46.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can't even bear it when people are sick around you.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:42.68,0:34:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你甚至不能忍受周围的人生病
Dialogue: 2,0:34:47.08,0:34:50.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Remember the times I had fevers as a kid?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:47.08,0:34:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还记得我小时候发烧吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.24,0:34:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Remember what you did? Do you remember?
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.24,0:34:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}记得你做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:53.68,0:34:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll remind you. You left.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:53.68,0:34:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我来提醒你！你离开了！
Dialogue: 2,0:34:57.52,0:34:59.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You left the house.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:57.52,0:34:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你离开了家
Dialogue: 2,0:34:59.64,0:35:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I used to pray with all my might not to get sick.
Dialogue: 2,0:34:59.64,0:35:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我曾经尽力祈祷不生病
Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.20,0:35:06.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not to get fevers so that my father didn't get mad at me.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.20,0:35:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要发烧，这样我的父亲就不会生我的气
Dialogue: 2,0:35:07.08,0:35:08.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You didn't look after mom, either.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:07.08,0:35:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你也没照顾妈妈
Dialogue: 2,0:35:09.12,0:35:12.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The nurses did. I did. father didn't get mad at me.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:09.12,0:35:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}护士照顾了，我和医生照顾了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:12.60,0:35:14.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But you never did.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:12.60,0:35:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你从来没有
Dialogue: 2,0:35:14.92,0:35:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'd come to the hospital.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:14.92,0:35:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你去医院
Dialogue: 2,0:35:17.12,0:35:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd tell you, "Dad, mom's dying."
Dialogue: 2,0:35:17.12,0:35:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会告诉你，“爸爸，妈妈快死了”
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.72,0:35:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'd say "No."
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.72,0:35:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你会说“不”
Dialogue: 2,0:35:21.24,0:35:24.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"She's doing great. Mom's doing great."
Dialogue: 2,0:35:21.24,0:35:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“她很好，妈妈很好”
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.20,0:35:26.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because that's what you want to hear.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.20,0:35:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为那是你想听到的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:27.16,0:35:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything's great. No problems whatsoever.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:27.16,0:35:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一切都很好没有任何问题
Dialogue: 2,0:35:30.00,0:35:32.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything's perfect.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:30.00,0:35:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一切都很完美
Dialogue: 2,0:35:32.68,0:35:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll say it if it will help. We have no problems, dad.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:32.68,0:35:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果有用的话，我就说出来  我们没问题，爸爸
Dialogue: 2,0:35:38.64,0:35:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're perfect. I'm perfect.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:38.64,0:35:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是完美的  我是完美的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:42.20,0:35:44.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Deva's perfect.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:42.20,0:35:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}德瓦也是完美的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:44.16,0:35:45.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Life's perfect.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:44.16,0:35:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}完美的人生
Dialogue: 2,0:35:49.76,0:35:50.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:49.76,0:35:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好
Dialogue: 2,0:35:51.44,0:35:52.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's good.
Dialogue: 2,0:35:51.44,0:35:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那很好
Dialogue: 2,0:36:05.16,0:36:06.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Agah Beyoglu.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:05.16,0:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里是阿加 贝尤鲁
Dialogue: 2,0:36:06.80,0:36:09.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Agah? - Nukhet!
Dialogue: 2,0:36:06.80,0:36:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-阿加？-努赫特！
Dialogue: 2,0:36:09.44,0:36:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How are you?
Dialogue: 2,0:36:09.44,0:36:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:11.48,0:36:13.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:11.48,0:36:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我刚刚还在想你
Dialogue: 2,0:36:13.60,0:36:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I was able to find some tickets.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:36:13.60,0:36:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我搞到了几张票
Dialogue: 2,0:36:15.24,0:36:18.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Were you now? - It's tonight. Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 2,0:36:15.24,0:36:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-是吗？-今天晚上你想一起吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:18.64,0:36:19.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:18.64,0:36:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:36:26.04,0:36:28.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- What is it? - We're ready.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:26.04,0:36:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-什么事？-我们准备好了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:28.32,0:36:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:28.32,0:36:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我马上到
Dialogue: 2,0:36:44.28,0:36:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hand these out to the guys.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:44.28,0:36:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把这些交给他们
Dialogue: 2,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Alright...
Dialogue: 2,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好了……
Dialogue: 2,0:36:55.92,0:36:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where's Nevra?
Dialogue: 2,0:36:55.92,0:36:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}内芙拉呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:57.64,0:37:01.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She got a tip from somewhere. She went to the courthouse to look into it.
Dialogue: 2,0:36:57.64,0:37:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她从某个地方得到了线报，去了法院进行调查
Dialogue: 2,0:37:01.60,0:37:04.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know Mehmet Yurtgil, the judge?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:01.60,0:37:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道穆罕默德·尤尔吉尔吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.08,0:37:05.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He was known for taking bribes.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.08,0:37:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他因受贿而闻名
Dialogue: 2,0:37:06.20,0:37:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She's looking into the suspects that were wronged.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:06.20,0:37:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她在调查被冤枉的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 2,0:37:08.32,0:37:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She thinks someone might've took revenge on him.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:08.32,0:37:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她认为有人可能会对他报仇
Dialogue: 2,0:37:12.72,0:37:14.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Alright then. Anyway,
Dialogue: 2,0:37:12.72,0:37:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好吧，不管怎样
Dialogue: 2,0:37:15.08,0:37:18.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have the ballistics report right here. Here's the situation:
Dialogue: 2,0:37:15.08,0:37:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我这里有弹道报告，结果是这样：
Dialogue: 2,0:37:18.32,0:37:22.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The gun that was used to kill Naimhan Turedi
Dialogue: 2,0:37:18.32,0:37:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用来杀死纳伊姆汉 ·图雷迪的枪
Dialogue: 2,0:37:22.08,0:37:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}does not match the one used to kill Mehmet Yurtgil.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:22.08,0:37:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与用来杀死穆罕默德·尤尔吉尔的那只不匹配
Dialogue: 2,0:37:24.64,0:37:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That gun wasn't registered anywhere. However...
Dialogue: 2,0:37:24.64,0:37:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那枪没有在任何地方注册
Dialogue: 2,0:37:28.56,0:37:32.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We have some leads on the gun that was used to kill Naimhan Turedi.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:28.56,0:37:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们在用来杀死纳伊姆汉 ·图雷迪的枪上有一些线索
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.12,0:37:35.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Someone was shot and wounded with that gun in 2001.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.12,0:37:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}2001年有人用那把枪开枪并受伤
Dialogue: 2,0:37:36.00,0:37:37.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The gun was seized, and is supposed to be
Dialogue: 2,0:37:36.00,0:37:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}枪应该是被没收了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:37.64,0:37:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in the Ardıchan municipality police department's evidence locker.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:37.64,0:37:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}存放在阿迪坎市警察局的证据储物柜中
Dialogue: 2,0:37:43.16,0:37:45.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But it's gone! Why's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:43.16,0:37:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是它消失了，为什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:45.40,0:37:48.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because that evidence locker no longer exists.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:45.40,0:37:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为那个证据储物柜已经没有了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:49.12,0:37:51.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How about... That sleazeball you were looking into?
Dialogue: 2,0:37:49.12,0:37:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你调查的那个混蛋怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:51.76,0:37:54.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 2,0:37:51.76,0:37:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他跟这些都没有关系
Dialogue: 2,0:37:55.44,0:37:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Alright. Now...
Dialogue: 2,0:37:55.44,0:37:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好吧……
Dialogue: 2,0:37:58.12,0:38:00.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The individual who did all this shit...
Dialogue: 2,0:37:58.12,0:38:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}做这些事的人
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.68,0:38:04.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's call him Tufan for now.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.68,0:38:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们暂时叫他图凡
Dialogue: 2,0:38:04.20,0:38:07.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Tufan gets into the evidence locker.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:04.20,0:38:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}图凡进入证据储物柜
Dialogue: 2,0:38:07.84,0:38:10.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He burglarizes the locker. Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:38:07.84,0:38:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他盗窃了储物柜，然后
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.76,0:38:14.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He burns the place down to make it look like the mafia did it.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.76,0:38:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他把地方烧了，使它看起来像黑手党做的一样
Dialogue: 2,0:38:15.04,0:38:18.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So he's not interested in killing just anyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:15.04,0:38:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以他对杀人不感兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:38:18.20,0:38:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's not a regular serial killer.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:18.20,0:38:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他不是常规的连环杀手
Dialogue: 2,0:38:20.28,0:38:21.89,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Since he's in possession of so many guns,
Dialogue: 2,0:38:20.28,0:38:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}既然他拥有这么多枪，
Dialogue: 2,0:38:21.92,0:38:24.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}and assuming he's not interested in selling them,
Dialogue: 2,0:38:21.92,0:38:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并假设他不准备卖枪
Dialogue: 2,0:38:24.48,0:38:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}welcome to your own personal hells.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:24.48,0:38:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那么就很明显了
Dialogue: 2,0:38:27.64,0:38:29.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's going to commit a massacre.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:27.64,0:38:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他将要开始屠杀
Dialogue: 2,0:38:33.24,0:38:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Unless we catch him first.
Dialogue: 2,0:38:33.24,0:38:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}除非我们先抓到他
Dialogue: 2,0:39:02.60,0:39:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}MARCH 18 SUNDAY
Dialogue: 2,0:39:02.60,0:39:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}3月18日 周日
Dialogue: 2,0:39:30.88,0:39:34.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Here. Here's my resumé.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:30.88,0:39:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是我的简历
Dialogue: 2,0:39:34.24,0:39:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Thank you for agreeing to see me. I know you're busy.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:34.24,0:39:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谢谢你同意见我  我知道你很忙
Dialogue: 2,0:39:38.88,0:39:41.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:38.88,0:39:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很荣幸见到你
Dialogue: 2,0:39:45.88,0:39:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This means nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:45.88,0:39:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这没什么意义
Dialogue: 2,0:39:52.40,0:39:53.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is it.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:52.40,0:39:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是这个
Dialogue: 2,0:39:54.36,0:39:57.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Where have you been? Austria? - Australia.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:54.36,0:39:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-您去过哪里？奥地利？-澳大利亚
Dialogue: 2,0:39:58.32,0:39:59.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I just got back.
Dialogue: 2,0:39:58.32,0:39:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我刚回来
Dialogue: 2,0:40:00.28,0:40:01.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're just in time.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:00.28,0:40:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你来的很及时
Dialogue: 2,0:40:03.48,0:40:05.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Melahat, my secretary for 20 years,
Dialogue: 2,0:40:03.48,0:40:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的秘书跟了我20年了，
Dialogue: 2,0:40:05.92,0:40:07.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}was retired just last week.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:05.92,0:40:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}上周刚刚退休
Dialogue: 2,0:40:09.40,0:40:11.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Coincidence, I guess.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:09.40,0:40:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我猜是巧合吧
Dialogue: 2,0:40:11.12,0:40:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There are no coincidences.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:11.12,0:40:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有巧合
Dialogue: 2,0:40:14.12,0:40:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because life itself is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:14.12,0:40:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为生活本身就是巧合
Dialogue: 2,0:40:18.32,0:40:20.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A man locks the door to his house for 99 days.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:18.32,0:40:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一个人连续锁门99天
Dialogue: 2,0:40:21.76,0:40:23.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On the 100th day, he forgets to lock the door.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:21.76,0:40:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在第100天，他忘记锁门
Dialogue: 2,0:40:24.84,0:40:26.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The thief repents.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:24.84,0:40:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小偷很后悔
Dialogue: 2,0:40:27.12,0:40:29.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He ignores the house for those 99 days,
Dialogue: 2,0:40:27.12,0:40:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在那99天内，他无视这所房子，
Dialogue: 2,0:40:29.80,0:40:32.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but finds the door unlocked on the 100th day.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:29.80,0:40:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但在第100天发现门没锁
Dialogue: 2,0:40:34.08,0:40:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The days line up.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:34.08,0:40:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都排着队
Dialogue: 2,0:40:41.80,0:40:42.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What do you call that?
Dialogue: 2,0:40:41.80,0:40:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你怎么说？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:44.88,0:40:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A coincidence?
Dialogue: 2,0:40:44.88,0:40:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}巧合？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:48.04,0:40:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:48.04,0:40:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是
Dialogue: 2,0:40:50.96,0:40:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:40:50.96,0:40:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:52.92,0:40:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's life.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:52.92,0:40:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这就是生活
Dialogue: 2,0:40:57.12,0:40:59.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're a fast learner, Zuhal.
Dialogue: 2,0:40:57.12,0:40:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你学得很快  祖哈尔
Dialogue: 2,0:41:00.28,0:41:03.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Celik. - Beyoglu. My surname's Beyoglu.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:00.28,0:41:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-塞利克 - 贝尤鲁  我姓贝尤鲁
Dialogue: 2,0:41:03.68,0:41:05.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm getting divorced.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:03.68,0:41:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要离婚了
Dialogue: 2,0:41:06.68,0:41:10.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you know Agah Beyoglu? Is he a relative of yours?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:06.68,0:41:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道阿加 贝尤鲁吗？他是你的亲戚吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's my father.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:12.12,0:41:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他是我父亲
Dialogue: 2,0:41:16.88,0:41:17.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Incredible.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:16.88,0:41:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}难以置信
Dialogue: 2,0:41:18.60,0:41:21.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Now this, this isn't life. This is coincidence.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:18.60,0:41:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这不是生命这是巧合
Dialogue: 2,0:41:21.76,0:41:24.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How is he doing? Well, I hope?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:21.76,0:41:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他最近好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:24.96,0:41:27.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's well, of course. How do you know him?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:24.96,0:41:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他很好，当然，你怎么认识他？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:28.96,0:41:31.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From Kambura. Where else?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:28.96,0:41:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然是坎布拉  还能是哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:48.08,0:41:50.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Prosecutor? - Did you know about this?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:48.08,0:41:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-检察官？-你知道这件事吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:51.52,0:41:53.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}KILLER OR VICTIM?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:51.52,0:41:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是杀手还是受害者？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:53.44,0:41:56.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I did. It was Nevra's idea. I told her to go ahead with it.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:53.44,0:41:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道  那是内芙拉的主意  我告诉她继续做下去
Dialogue: 2,0:41:57.08,0:41:59.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That was a stupid risk to take.
Dialogue: 2,0:41:57.08,0:41:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是一个愚蠢的冒险
Dialogue: 2,0:41:59.08,0:42:02.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What if Tufan gets caught and everything is revealed?
Dialogue: 2,0:41:59.08,0:42:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果图凡被抓了并且一切都暴露了怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:02.60,0:42:03.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What then?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:02.60,0:42:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然后会怎样呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:04.80,0:42:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Tufan has no connection either to Nevra or to any of the victims.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:04.80,0:42:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}图凡与内芙拉或任何受害者都没有任何关系
Dialogue: 2,0:42:10.20,0:42:12.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's why I approved the news article.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:10.20,0:42:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我批准了这篇新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:42:12.24,0:42:14.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's someone else involved.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:12.24,0:42:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有其他人参与
Dialogue: 2,0:42:14.16,0:42:15.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Whoever it is that's helping Tufan
Dialogue: 2,0:42:14.16,0:42:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管是谁在帮图凡
Dialogue: 2,0:42:16.00,0:42:18.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}will panic when he realizes that we're on his trail.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:16.00,0:42:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当他意识到我们在追踪他时，他会感到恐慌
Dialogue: 2,0:42:19.96,0:42:21.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's your call.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:19.96,0:42:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你的电话
Dialogue: 2,0:42:21.96,0:42:23.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But I'm uneasy.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:21.96,0:42:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可是我很不安
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.84,0:42:28.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm not sure getting Nevra involved in this was the right idea.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.84,0:42:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不确定让内芙拉参与这个案子是否正确
Dialogue: 2,0:42:28.36,0:42:31.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you have any better ideas? No?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:28.36,0:42:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您有更好的主意吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:31.08,0:42:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then we proceed.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:31.08,0:42:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那我们继续
Dialogue: 2,0:42:33.68,0:42:34.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Did you tell Firuz?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:33.68,0:42:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你有没有告诉菲鲁兹？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.88,0:42:36.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I did. He's supervising Nevra.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.88,0:42:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}告诉他了  他在监督内芙拉
Dialogue: 2,0:42:36.96,0:42:38.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where's Nevra now?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:36.96,0:42:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}内芙拉现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.60,0:42:41.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told her she'd be kicked off the force if it was discovered.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.60,0:42:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我告诉她如果被发现  她会被踢出警队
Dialogue: 2,0:42:41.72,0:42:45.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She's lying to me. Told me her mom was sick. Went to Kambura.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:41.72,0:42:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她对我撒谎  告诉我她妈妈生病了  去了坎布拉
Dialogue: 2,0:42:46.20,0:42:47.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's where she lives.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:46.20,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是她家
Dialogue: 2,0:42:48.20,0:42:51.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Isn't there where the second victim was born?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:48.20,0:42:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}第二个受害者不就是在那里出生的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:51.08,0:42:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's right. She could be looking into it.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:51.08,0:42:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是的  她可能正在调查
Dialogue: 2,0:42:54.00,0:42:56.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Good. We have some leads, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:54.00,0:42:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好  我们有了一些线索
Dialogue: 2,0:42:57.00,0:43:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We do but I can't bear the thought of using one of my people as bait.
Dialogue: 2,0:42:57.00,0:43:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我不忍心用我的人当诱饵
Dialogue: 2,0:43:02.96,0:43:06.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you having her followed? You are. So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 2,0:43:02.96,0:43:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是有人在跟着她吗？有什么不放心的？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:06.92,0:43:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Look here, Tolga.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:06.92,0:43:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}注意  托尔加
Dialogue: 2,0:43:08.08,0:43:10.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He's not going to stop killing people anytime soon.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:08.08,0:43:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他近期不会停止杀人
Dialogue: 2,0:43:10.80,0:43:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Who's supposed to catch him? You are.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:10.80,0:43:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁应该抓住他？是你
Dialogue: 2,0:43:12.76,0:43:14.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What's the only lead we have? Nevra.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:12.76,0:43:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唯一的线索是什么？内芙拉
Dialogue: 2,0:43:14.80,0:43:17.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you take Nevra off the case,
Dialogue: 2,0:43:14.80,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你将内芙拉拒之门外，
Dialogue: 2,0:43:17.84,0:43:20.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}it won't matter whether it was Tufan or someone else.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:17.84,0:43:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管是图凡还是其他人
Dialogue: 2,0:43:20.60,0:43:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll never catch the murderer.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:20.60,0:43:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你永远都不会抓住凶手
Dialogue: 2,0:43:22.92,0:43:26.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Someone's committing these murders just to get Nevra to try to solve them.
Dialogue: 2,0:43:22.92,0:43:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人犯下这些谋杀罪只是为了让内夫拉设法解决他们
Dialogue: 2,0:43:48.64,0:43:51.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}MAYA'S COSTUME WORLD
Dialogue: 2,0:43:48.64,0:43:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}玛雅的装扮世界
Dialogue: 2,0:44:34.24,0:44:36.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Those things will kill you, you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:34.24,0:44:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烟会杀死你的，你知道吧
Dialogue: 2,0:44:36.56,0:44:39.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You don't have to throw it out. Give me one.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:36.56,0:44:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}别扔，给我来一支
Dialogue: 2,0:44:42.88,0:44:45.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Any leads from the courthouse? - No.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:42.88,0:44:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-法院有线索了吗？-没有
Dialogue: 2,0:44:47.16,0:44:48.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have a light.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:47.16,0:44:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我有火
Dialogue: 2,0:44:49.60,0:44:51.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My father's lighter.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:49.60,0:44:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我父亲的打火机
Dialogue: 2,0:44:52.72,0:44:54.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}He passed it down to me the day he stopped smoking.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:52.72,0:44:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他戒烟的那一天把它传给了我
Dialogue: 2,0:44:55.04,0:44:58.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I asked him what I was supposed to do with it. I didn't even smoke.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:55.04,0:44:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我问他我该怎么办，我那时还没开始抽烟
Dialogue: 2,0:44:58.40,0:44:59.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I picked it up that day.
Dialogue: 2,0:44:58.40,0:44:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在那天开始抽烟
Dialogue: 2,0:45:00.64,0:45:03.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I picked up smoking the day my father quit. Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:00.64,0:45:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我父亲戒烟那一天我开始抽烟
Dialogue: 2,0:45:06.72,0:45:09.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was my mom that encouraged me to smoke, actually.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:06.72,0:45:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}实际上是我妈妈鼓励我抽烟
Dialogue: 2,0:45:09.52,0:45:14.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She told me it was alright if I smoked, but that I shouldn't be sneaky about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:09.52,0:45:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她告诉我如果我抽烟是可以的，但是不应该偷偷摸摸
Dialogue: 2,0:45:15.12,0:45:17.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't smoke, but I couldn't tell her.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:15.12,0:45:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不会抽烟，但是我不能告诉她
Dialogue: 2,0:45:20.48,0:45:24.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I sat across from her and lit one up just to get to spend some time with her.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:20.48,0:45:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我坐在她的对面，点燃了一根烟，与她共度时光
Dialogue: 2,0:45:26.60,0:45:28.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's how I started smoking.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:26.60,0:45:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我就是这样开始吸烟的
Dialogue: 2,0:45:28.16,0:45:30.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just to do the same thing as her at the same time as she did.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:28.16,0:45:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只是为了和她在一起做点什么事
Dialogue: 2,0:45:32.84,0:45:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How is she? Better?
Dialogue: 2,0:45:32.84,0:45:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:35.84,0:45:37.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Better. She's better.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:35.84,0:45:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好多了
Dialogue: 2,0:45:37.52,0:45:40.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It must be hard, living so far away from each other.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:37.52,0:45:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}应该很难吧，彼此相距太远
Dialogue: 2,0:45:41.56,0:45:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I see her from time to time. - Good. Don't stop seeing her.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:41.56,0:45:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我时不时能见到她 -好  不要不见她
Dialogue: 2,0:45:44.92,0:45:46.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My father's dead now.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:44.92,0:45:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我父亲已经死了
Dialogue: 2,0:45:47.04,0:45:48.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is all that's left of him.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:47.04,0:45:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这就是他剩下的一切
Dialogue: 2,0:45:56.00,0:45:56.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}MUNIR - MY LOVELY CAT
Dialogue: 2,0:45:56.00,0:45:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尼穆尔 -我可爱的猫
Dialogue: 2,0:45:56.84,0:45:58.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm so scared of death, Munir.
Dialogue: 2,0:45:56.84,0:45:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我好怕死，穆尼尔
Dialogue: 2,0:46:00.48,0:46:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In fact, I'll tell you a secret.
Dialogue: 2,0:46:00.48,0:46:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其实我会告诉你一个秘密
Dialogue: 2,0:46:03.76,0:46:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd be OK with it even if everyone on earth died
Dialogue: 2,0:46:03.76,0:46:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使地球上的每个人都死了，我也没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:46:06.76,0:46:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}and I were the only one left.
Dialogue: 2,0:46:06.76,0:46:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是唯一剩下的一个
Dialogue: 2,0:46:10.80,0:46:11.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:46:10.80,0:46:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的意思是
Dialogue: 2,0:46:13.44,0:46:15.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm even willing to face such loneliness.
Dialogue: 2,0:46:13.44,0:46:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我甚至愿意面对这样的寂寞
Dialogue: 2,0:46:17.52,0:46:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What if I still remember all I've done in the afterlife?
Dialogue: 2,0:46:17.52,0:46:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果我来世还记得我所做的一切怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:22.08,0:46:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I couldn't bear that.
Dialogue: 2,0:46:22.08,0:46:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不能忍受
Dialogue: 2,0:46:25.32,0:46:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I couldn't.
Dialogue: 2,0:46:25.32,0:46:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不能
