Dialogue: 2,0:50:54.80,0:50:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看！你弄坏了，赔钱吧
Dialogue: 2,0:51:08.44,0:51:11.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Forgive me, Hajji. - It's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:51:08.44,0:51:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-请原谅哈吉（到麦加朝圣过的伊斯兰教徒）  -算了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:11.16,0:51:13.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I have to follow the orders. - I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:51:11.16,0:51:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我必须遵守命令  -我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:51:13.80,0:51:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My uncle's a Hajji as well. He just got back.
Dialogue: 2,0:51:13.80,0:51:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我叔叔也是哈吉  他刚回来
Dialogue: 2,0:51:15.72,0:51:17.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}May Allah bless him.
Dialogue: 2,0:51:15.72,0:51:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿真主保佑他
Dialogue: 2,0:51:17.72,0:51:18.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Amen. Amen.
