Dialogue: 2,0:51:44.44,0:51:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-别说了  你现在到了  -看起来很棒
Dialogue: 2,0:51:47.76,0:51:49.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Thank you. So do you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:51:47.76,0:51:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-谢谢你  你也是  -谢谢
